{"tid":886292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[優良傳統] 盧偉聰:警隊優良傳統薪火相傳","createTime":"2018-11-02T03:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T04:45:01.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"393c1ad5974e70ceed4f3f9e9d333490aaab624b","tid":886292,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:51:50.000Z","msg":"警方今日舉行紀念日，悼念執行職務期間殉職的警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰致詞時表示，對過去174年來盡忠職守的警務人員表示最崇高敬意，警務工作充滿危險性和不確定性，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警隊優良傳統將薪火相傳，成為世界上其中一支最優秀執法隊伍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰連同警隊主要單位，為殉職警員默哀，警隊的多個協會代表分別獻上花圈致敬。<br />\n<br />\n警隊的3本榮譽名冊內，共紀錄369名殉職警員及輔警名單。"},{"pid":"460ac3666567e5245991ff6a4dc446375abfc117","tid":886292,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"369<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a382ec36baed28ba7288ff5420b2f6e750e304","tid":886292,"uid":66514,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170224/large/a0201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170224%2Flarge%2Fa0201a.gif&h=6566d958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f293c8ad369e4e040bb8240a16e660042eb7fbd5","tid":886292,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460ac3666567e5245991ff6a4dc446375abfc117","tid":886292,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"369<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:54:43.000Z","msg":"m9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9897ec0bb4fcf468f24e97740a9fa019587eb33","tid":886292,"uid":182314,"like":4,"dislik